{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：08:32 2026-04-23 HKT<br/>發佈時間：08:32 2026-04-23 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：08:32 2026-04-23 HKT</p><img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl_square/40f02d3db4a6f741fe8d5f483b0a4375/2026-04/page_178.jpg\"/><p>葵涌有的士失事翻側。今日（23日）早上7時07，一輛「小露寶」的士在和宜合道近金威工業大廈對開「自炒」失事，繼而向右翻側橫亙在路上。救援人員接報指司機及男乘客被困於車上，幸最後兩人獲救脫困，同由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。意外原因有待調查。</p><img alt=\"的士失事翻側。黎志偉攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/6308e50b61b5d08fad6ef9030ceb24c6/2026-04/1_24.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/ff3d7575bbc1901d0f98851895d08e2c/2026-04/2_1_10.jpg\"/><img alt=\"的士翻側橫亙在路中。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/3fc0fabafe57d20aaa66a15d934cc8a0/2026-04/3_4_10.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/bc0556f20c2ae9ddf7fd6705d1226eb2/2026-04/4_5_5.jpg\"/><img alt=\"警員在場調查。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/10772b5ad03f1edd252f314bb18ddc5c/2026-04/5_3_6.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/7c41ec5ca755004079719405410edeb5/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260423_075057732_02.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/3339b7e66061239d33fe36befd2a867b/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260423_075057732_08.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/072760485b7b8ada0c5a9ccb46758a52/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260423_075057732_09.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T00:44:57.750841+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":202,"images":9,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}